{"tid":1526562,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家仲睇漏野未制裁黑警","createTime":"2019-09-01T06:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T18:07:14.000Z","uid":247494,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8c60b88829558217014d501473c31de439664f42","tid":1526562,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"黑警Turn out rate 咁高，幾乎抽調8成人出狗屋，剩番的人係咩？？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">老差骨同埋輔警！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n先講一講輔警係咩，佢地多數有份正職，輔警就係份兼職。佔中時期，狗屋經常開好多VDO來俾輔警番工，等黑警毫無忌憚地出去，今次亦都係咁樣。尼班人日頭做咩，絕大多數係做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府，老師！</span><br />\n<br />\n更甚的是，老個批輔警係有埋外國護照，有咩事就著草<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地口口聲聲話維持治安，但係返狗屋幫黑警打市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地必須釜底抽薪，搞鳩輔警日頭份工，到時狗屋冇人幫就加快佢地崩潰！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQAzEub.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQAzEub.jpg&h=72d293d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面活動，大家到時識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n輔警好多時係各大U搞招募活動，我相信大家唔會忘記721 及831<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家供出身邊咩人做輔警！因為本人見尋晚單野實在太嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c006d76dc2b0ca374416d962333282d91c7ef028","tid":1526562,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:01:58.000Z","msg":"Push push push"},{"pid":"52d17b846350c8d47a5d3a093eaec2b283eeeb9b","tid":1526562,"uid":57868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:06:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ae75649e90fa5d95a0efe945abd5dd37fb0d7f5e","tid":1526562,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:07:28.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"46377f3a36f289ecfe31873a2c10de9beeded4bb","tid":1526562,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:08:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f6c84fff2335d57ae372b0719150e400fb6129d","tid":1526562,"uid":160131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cf4b0bb3a88eda60bed8390b932112e3755b5c2","tid":1526562,"uid":247494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7xvHdKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7xvHdKE.jpg&h=3918dca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又一個輔狗"},{"pid":"de83d9c37bd0cdbf218e3015fccfd8612313b02b","tid":1526562,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:02:40.000Z","msg":"[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪 [國難老闆同一眾員工已保釋,開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0bb41cf8b3a0f0b12bb655e0ce9a795dc131d6","tid":1526562,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:39:21.000Z","msg":"Push push push push"},{"pid":"85992614b79200976423f22599184832ad6308e1","tid":1526562,"uid":234826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:43:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b127edda83d8b04557181863a20816ae79fefcf","tid":1526562,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:47:35.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"067f26a3ac88f6dff0c5f98ccf68a3bb3b7ca9eb","tid":1526562,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:29:36.000Z","msg":"Push push push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b501f91075b95b46b2fcbb8425d5644768cc173","tid":1526562,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:28:14.000Z","msg":"又一個輔狗<br />\n<br />\nA8692 嚴偉光"},{"pid":"b303eaa84b30c9e2b911ce79e613c2df47803c8e","tid":1526562,"uid":88768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:29:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">太子殺人犯</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"f